instruction: Hello, I am Maria Patterson from Auburn, WA (zip 98002) with BowlerID 34. Please verify my identity to proceed. Once verified, I want to set my handicap to 25 and update my total pins to 100 because I just bowled my first practice game and scored 100 pins. Also, set up a practice tournament: TourneyID=1 at Auburn Bowling Center on 2024-07-10. Schedule match MatchID=101 on lanes '5-6' with my team (TeamID=7) as OddLaneTeamID and the opposing team (TeamID=8) as EvenLaneTeamID. For this match, record GameNumber=1 with BowlerID=34, RawScore=100, HandiCapScore=125, and mark that I won and my team won. Update all records accordingly.

actions.sql: SELECT BowlerFirstName, BowlerLastName, BowlerCity, BowlerZip FROM Bowlers WHERE BowlerID=34;
UPDATE Bowlers SET BowlerCurrentHcp=25, BowlerTotalPins=100, BowlerGamesBowled=1 WHERE BowlerID=34;
INSERT INTO Tournaments (TourneyID, TourneyDate, TourneyLocation) VALUES (1, '2024-07-10', 'Auburn Bowling Center');
INSERT INTO Tourney_Matches (MatchID, TourneyID, Lanes, OddLaneTeamID, EvenLaneTeamID) VALUES (101, 1, '5-6', 7, 8);
INSERT INTO Bowler_Scores (MatchID, GameNumber, BowlerID, RawScore, HandiCapScore, WonGame) VALUES (101, 1, 34, 100, 125, TRUE);
INSERT INTO Match_Games (MatchID, GameNumber, WinningTeamID) VALUES (101, 1, 7);
